Japan, China, Philippines, Thailand: Asia Local Bond and Currency Preview

-- B y   Y u m i   T e s o
-- 
2011-03-17T21:58:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-17/japan-china-philippines-thailand-asia-local-bond-and-currency-preview.html
The following events and economic
reports may influence trading in  Asia ’s bonds and currencies
today. Bond yields and exchange rates are from the previous
trading session unless stated otherwise.  Japan: Chief Cabinet Secretary Yukio Edano and Finance
Minister  Yoshihiko Noda  will hold media briefings after a
Cabinet meeting in the morning. Edano will have another press
briefing at 4 p.m. in Tokyo.  The  Bank of Japan  will release at 8:50 a.m. in Tokyo
minutes of its Feb. 14-15 board meeting.  The yield on the 1.3 percent government bond due March 2021
was 1.20 percent, according to Japan Bond Trading Co., the
nation’s largest interdealer debt broker.  The yen traded at 79.07 per dollar at 6:52 a.m. in Tokyo.    China : A report on property prices in China in February is
due today. New home prices rose in all but two of the 70 cities
monitored by the government in January from a year earlier.
Prices advanced 6.8 percent in Beijing and 1.5 percent in
Shanghai.  The yield on the government’s 3.77 percent bond due
December 2020 was 3.87 percent. The yuan was at 6.5755.    Philippines : The central bank will release the balance of
payments position for February today. The country posted a
surplus of $1.6 billion in January.  The yield on the 6.25 percent bond due January 2014 was
5.15 percent, according to Tradition Financial Services. The
peso was at 43.888.    Thailand : Foreign-exchange reserves data for the week ended
March 11 is due today. The holdings rose 0.9 percent to $180.8
billion the previous week.  The central bank will sell 15 billion baht ($495 million)
of two-year floating-rate notes and 85 billion baht of 14-day
bills.  The yield on the 3.125 percent debt due December 2015 was
3.32 percent. The baht was at 30.29.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Yumi Teso in Bangkok at 
